Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（约翰・C・德普二世诉 安柏点劳拉点赫德案审理历时六周）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（从2022年4月开始）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（德普和赫德间隔两周出庭作证）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（为便于理解 两场庭审的录像被剪辑在一起）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（这是他们的证词 第一次被并排展示）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你连海湾都出不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll never make it out of the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Son,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是杰克・斯派洛船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Captain Jack Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Savvy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是好莱坞最大最成功的明星之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's one of Hollywood's biggest and most successful stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演员约翰尼・德普和安柏・赫德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Actors Johnny Depp and Amber Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼！安柏！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny! Johnny and Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-约翰尼！ -安柏！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Johnny! - Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在距离好莱坞的 浮华和魅力几百公里的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hundreds of miles away from the glitz and glamour of Hollywood...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普 对其前妻安柏・赫德的诽谤案审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp's defamation trial against his ex-wife, Amber Heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即将在北弗吉尼亚州开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is set to start in northern Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防你看肥皂剧太入迷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just in case you've gotten lost in the soap opera,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普声称安柏・赫德诽谤他 索赔5000万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}50 million dollar claim by Johnny Depp that Amber Heard defamed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2018年 她在《华盛顿邮报》上写了一篇评论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She wrote a 2018 op-ed in The Washington Post
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指出自己是代表家庭暴力的公众人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}referring to herself as a public figure representing domestic abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普和他的法律团队 声称赫德完全是撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Depp and his legal team say that Heard is outright lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且那些谎言毁了他的事业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and that those lies have devastated his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德反诉要求赔偿一亿美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Heard countersued for 100 million in damages,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声称该演员的法律团队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}alleging the actor's legal team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试图通过称她的主张为骗局来诽谤她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}tried to defame her by calling her claims a hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普和赫德都不曾 在弗吉尼亚州生活或工作过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Neither Depp nor Heard live or work here in Virginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因为《华盛顿邮报》 在这里有服务器和打印机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but because The Washington Post has servers here and a printer here in Virginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费尔法克斯县的居民将决定他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fairfax County residents are gonna decide their fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个5000万美元案件中的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in this 50 million dollar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《德普 vs 赫德： 好莱坞夫妻诽谤案》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剧名：《第一集：真相审判》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（2022年4月 弗吉尼亚）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在前往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right now, I am on my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费尔法克斯县法院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the Fairfax County Courthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去排队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to get into line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（达斯新闻）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普庭审的第一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}] Day one of the Johnny Depp trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有100名观众\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's gonna be 100 spectators,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括媒体、市民、支持者和粉丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it's gonna be a mix of media and just civilians, you know, supporters, fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说是先到先得 所以我得早点去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hear it's first come, first serve. So gotta be there bright and early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得拿出这个抱枕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, wait, I gotta take a picture of the cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我要拿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, okay, I'm going for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱你们 传下去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you guys. Pass it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把镜头翻过来 这样你们就能看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's flip it up so you guys can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-早上好 -早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排队的大家感觉如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How are we feeling, line?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带话题“尊重队伍”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hashtag "respect for the line."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“为排队正名”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Justice for the line."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是官方媒体 就必须在街那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so if you're, like, official media, you have to be on that side of the street, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你只是粉丝 你可以来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you're, like, just a fan, you can be over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我可以更近距离地看约翰尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I can kind of get, like, a closer look at Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普起诉他的前妻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp is suing his ex-wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏・赫德 赔偿5000万美元损失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber Heard, for 50 million dollars in damages,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他诉称遭到她诽谤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}claiming she defamed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 作为一线演员 约翰尼・德普和其前妻安柏・赫德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Welcome back. We're getting a closer look into the lives of Hollywood's elites
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诽谤案的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as part of the defamation lawsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要进一步了解好莱坞精英的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}between A-lister Johnny Depp and ex-wife Amber Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（安德鲁・蒂姆伯特 ABC新闻主播）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2020年 德普在与一家 英国小报的诉讼中败诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In 2020, Depp lost a lawsuit against a British tabloid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该小报称他“殴打妻子”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that labeled him a, quote, "wife-beater."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和赫德都要在 这次审判中出庭作证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He and Heard are both expected to testify at this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人都在谈论这场庭审 有很多直播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lots of people are talking about this, I know there's lots of livestreams happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自己看庭审并形成自己的意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can go watch the trial yourself, make your own opinions of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网上都有 去YouTube看就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's online. You can go to YouTube right now and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼 我们爱你！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny, we love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的节目比较特别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Today is a different kind of show
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们要观看 约翰尼・德普对安柏・赫德案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because we are going to be watching the opening statements
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的开庭陈述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the Johnny Depp-Amber Heard case
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并边观看边评述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and going through them with commentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我拿到了旁观通行证 太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, so I got my spectator pass. That is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（达斯新闻 YouTube博主）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（约翰C德普）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们上了五楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so we are up here on the fifth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的庭审将在这里开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's where his trial's taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能用手机 我不应该在这里录像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not supposed to be on our phones. Definitely not supposed to be recording up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有安柏・赫德的粉丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no Amber Heard fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有约翰尼・德普的粉丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's only... It's only Johnny Depp fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没人支持安柏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody's there for Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's up, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到法律解释 我希望你们准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Welcome to Lawsplaining, and I hope you are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（播放量 评论）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是首批进入庭审的备受瞩目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is one of the first high-profile "Me Too" defamation cases
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我也是”诽谤案之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's making it into a courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是大新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is huge news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（雷吉塔法律）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 来了 这就是主角本人 约翰尼D\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, there we are. There's the man himself, Johnny D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那条领带不错 我喜欢那条领带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a nice tie! I like that tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好迎接陪审团了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Ready for the jury? - Yes, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 法官大人 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法院电视台和其他电视台 为什么能被允许转播庭审呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So how is it that Court TV and other stations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are even allowed to broadcast this trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们能像这样 进入费尔法克斯县法院？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why do we have such crazy access into the Fairfax County Courthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在弗吉尼亚州 这件事的决定权完全在于法官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In Virginia, that decision is solely up to the judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该案的法官签署了一项指令 允许摄像机转播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the judge in this case signed an order permitting a pool camera to broadcast the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（佩妮・阿兹卡瑞特法官 费尔法克斯县巡回法院）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们 先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将明确你们作为本案陪审员的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we're gonna go over the responsibilities you have as jurors, okay, in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不能在任何 社交网站上阅读、观看或收听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, so you're not to read, watch, or listen to anything about this case
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与本案相关的任何信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}on any social networking sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们得到的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What you learn about this case
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅限于在这个法庭内得知的全部信息 好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is limited to what you learn in the four walls of this courtroom. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开庭陈述？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are we ready with opening statements?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官在要求德普的律师做开庭陈述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The judge is asking for Johnny Depp's attorney's opening statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要切换成全屏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, I'm gonna cut to a full screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有停顿的话 我会进行评述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I will chime in with some commentary if there are some breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始了 来自弗吉尼亚的爆米花星球的直播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But here we go, live, uh, on Popcorned Planet here in Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-早上好 -早\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good morning. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一起诽谤案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a defamation case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个案件是关于 当虚假言辞被公开说出时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a case about how devastating words can be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其破坏性可以有多么巨大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when they are false and uttered publicly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近30年来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For nearly 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生被誉为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp built a reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好莱坞最有才华的男演员之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as one of the most talented actors in Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今 他的名字与一个谎言关联\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Today, his name is associated with a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由他前妻撒出的谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}uttered by his former wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是被告 安柏・赫德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the defendant, Amber Heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具体而言 是她在2018年12月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}specifically the words that she used
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公开发表在《华盛顿邮报》上的言辞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}published in The Washington Post in December 2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“两年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Quote, "Two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我成为了代表家庭暴力的公众人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I became a public figure representing domestic abuse."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个难得的有利条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I had the rare vantage point
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以实时看到 机构如何保护被指控虐待的男性”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of seeing in real time how institutions protect men accused of abuse."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐没有在评论中引用德普先生的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ms. Heard did not use Mr. Depp's name in the op-ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不必引用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two years earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐公开指责约翰尼・德普家庭暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ms. Heard had publicly accused Johnny Depp of domestic abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（2016年5月 洛杉矶）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏 是约翰尼造成的你脸上的淤青吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber, did Johnny give you that bruise on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普跟女演员安柏・赫德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp accused of domestic abuse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然分手 被指控有家庭暴力行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in his sudden split from actress Amber Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼有没有对你施暴？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did Johnny brutalize you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着“我也是”运动的兴起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the wake of the Me Too movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏・赫德彻底改变了 德普先生的生活和声誉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber Heard forever changed Mr. Depp's life and reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次庭审是为了洗清德普先生的名誉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This trial is about clearing Mr. Depp's name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让其免受可怕的虚假指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of a terrible and false allegation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗腾伯恩先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Rottenborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以上前吗？ -可以 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- May I approach? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-大家早上好 -早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good morning, everyone. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生的团队 会试图把这个案子变成一部肥皂剧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp's team is gonna try to turn this case into a soap opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？我不太确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why? I'm not really sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为证据对德普先生很不利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because the evidence isn't pretty for Mr. Depp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们会看到约翰尼・德普的真面目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're gonna see who the real Johnny Depp is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在名声和海盗装束的背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}behind the fame, behind the pirate costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个将自己的暴力面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The man who has described himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,描述为“怪物”的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the violent side of himself, as "the monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“怪物”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"The monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《华盛顿邮报》没有出现在这个法庭的被告席上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't see The Washington Post sitting here as a defendant in this courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只起诉了安柏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He only sued Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他本来可以起诉《华盛顿邮报》 文章是他们发表的 但他没有这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He could've sued The Washington Post, they published the article, but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他选择让安柏出席在弗吉尼亚的庭审\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he chose to bring Amber to court here in Virginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里孤立无援\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where she has no ties,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没有在这里生活过 他也没有 他们俩都没有在这里待过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has never lived, he's never lived, where they never spent any time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他想毁了她的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because he wanted to ruin her life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纠缠她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to haunt her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁她的事业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to wreck her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点不在于 德普会把本案变成的肥皂剧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not about the soap opera that Depp will turn this case into.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在于你更喜欢谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not about who you like better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不在于你是否同意她写出的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not even about whether you agree with the words that she wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点在于她说那些话的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's about her right to speak them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（赫德：我大声疾呼反对性暴力）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（直面了我们文化的愤怒 这种情况必须改变）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（抖音）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普有一支最优秀的法律团队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp has one of the most brilliant legal teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要证据 我可以给你一个词 “弗吉尼亚”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and if you need proof of that, I've got a word for you, "Virginia."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么两个来自加利福尼亚的名人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would two celebrities from California
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,争论《华盛顿邮报》上发表的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}arguing about something written in The Washington Post
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会在弗吉尼亚州立案？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}file a case in Virginia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在美国 诽谤法因州而异\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the USA, defamation laws vary state by state,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而弗吉尼亚州有最好的诽谤法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Virginia has some of the best defamation laws for a matter like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们意见一致 这不是离婚案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just so we're all on the same page, this is not a divorce case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是家庭暴力案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is not a domestic violence case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是伪装成诽谤案的公关活动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would argue it's a PR campaign disguised as a defamation case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得约翰尼的目的不是打赢官司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think Johnny's intention is to win the case here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他的目的是洗清他的名声 控制自己的声誉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think his intention is to clear his name and to control his reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何公关活动有机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There is no PR campaign that has a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,产生像这次庭审一样大的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of making an impact as powerful as this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（布莱恩・卡伦 喜剧演员和演员 PDB播客嘉宾）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是德普想让摄像机进法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Depp was the one who wanted the cameras in the courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不想要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的第一个证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your first witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想请劳拉安柏・赫德出庭作证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Honor, we'd like to call Laura Amber Heard to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能说出你的名字吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you please state your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我是安柏・劳拉・希德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, it's Amber Laura Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你为什么来这里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来是因为我的前夫 因为我写的文章起诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am here because my ex-husband is suing me, uh, for an op-ed I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对此有何感受？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And how do you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很难找到词汇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, um...I s... struggle to have the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很难找到描述这件事有多痛苦的词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I struggle to find the words to describe how, uh, painful this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, this is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 请说吧 女士？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, all right. Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好 德普先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good afternoon, Mr. Depp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉陪审团 你今天为什么来这里吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you please tell the jury why you're here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约六年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About six years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐提出了一些 针对我的令人发指的指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ms. Heard made some quite heinous accusations against me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些指控没有任何形式的事实依据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that, uh...that were not based in any species of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那张臭名昭著的《人物》杂志封面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The infamous People Magazine cover with Ms. Heard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐脸上有深色淤青\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with a... a dark bruise on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有发生过这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing of the kind had ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们有一些…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Though there were...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,争论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（法庭证据 录音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这可没用 你这个傻逼！ -你太幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-成熟点吧 -给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先听我说 然后你可以回应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我从来没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But never did I, myself, r... reach the point
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到对赫德小姐动手的地步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of, um, striking Ms. Heard in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也从来没有攻击过任何女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}nor have I ever struck, um, any woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没发现这里有人 我以为它只是浮着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't realize anyone was there, I thought it was just... floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的确只是浮着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is just floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她要出现？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why did she have to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前没有她 我也过得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just when I was doing so good without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请为陪审团描述一下 你试镜《朗姆酒日记》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please describe for the jury your experience in auditioning
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时候的经历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for The Rum Diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我参加了几次试镜 这在我的工作中很常见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I auditioned a few times, which is common in my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我接到一个电话 说约翰尼想亲自见我一面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then I got a call saying that Johnny wanted to meet me in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我可能是去试镜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought I would be going for maybe an audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是开会而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um... But it was just a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去他办公室跟他见了几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I went to his office, um, and... and met with him for a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她来了我办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She came to my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了一眼 心想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took one look at her and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“是的 就是她了”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Yep, that's the one."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我第一次见赫德小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's when I first met Ms. Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们聊了书、音乐和诗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We talked about books and music, poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有很多相同的爱好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, we like a lot of the same...We liked a lot of the same stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很惊讶有一个人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was so surprised that somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个无名小演员 我当时应该22岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, I'm a no-name actor. I was 22, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他年龄是我的两倍 而且他是闻名于世的演员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he was twice my age and he's this world-famous actor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们都喜欢老的布鲁斯音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and here we are getting along about......old blues,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时认为这很不寻常 很了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I thought it was unusual and remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我离开的时候感觉：“哇哦”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I left there just feeling like, "Wow."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得有场戏是我在淋浴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember there was a scene where I was taking a shower
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她走进房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then she comes into the room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她走过来 打开淋浴间 然后我们接吻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she walks, opens the shower, and we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让我产生了不该产生的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It felt like something that I shouldn't be feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:14:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工作过程中 你要做出一些能彰显专业性的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are certain things that you do in the job to, um, be professional,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如当你演那种类型的戏时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like when you have to do that sort of scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要尽量避免使用你的舌头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you don't, like... you......you don't use your tongue if you can't... if you can avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了保持边界感 有些事是不能做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's certain things that you do to just maintain a certain line,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得那条边界被模糊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it just felt like those lines were blurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他抓住我的头 把我拉过去 真的亲吻了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, he grabbed my face and pulled me into him and really kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他用舌头了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did he use his tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天下班后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That day after work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐来到了我的拖车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ms. Heard, uh, had come to my trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他开玩笑地把我推倒在他拖车里的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He kind of playfully kind of pushed me down on this, like, bed-sofa,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙发床上 像开玩笑一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}uh, that was in his trailer, just playful,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些调戏意味 然后他说：“真美味”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}um, and flirtatious, and he said, uh, "Yum."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到安柏・赫德这样的演员 她像是另一个时代的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Meeting an actress like Amber Heard, she's of another era, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就像走进一个房间 见到维罗妮卡・雷克或贝蒂・戴维斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, it's like walking into a room and meeting Veronica Lake or Bette Davis,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是劳伦・巴考尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or, you know, Lauren Bacall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我管她叫“苗条”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I called her "Slim."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫她“苗条” 她叫我“史蒂夫”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I called her "Slim" and she called me "Steve."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你要怎么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think you're gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿到那个钱包 苗条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna get that wallet, Slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的 史蒂夫 我对你不能完全放心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, Steve, I wouldn't put it past you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天亨弗莱・鲍嘉和劳伦・巴考尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My God, when Humphrey Bogart and Lauren Bacall,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是在那部电影里认识的 他45岁 而她19岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's when they met, on that film, he was 45 years old and she was 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么那么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What'd you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我一直在想我是否会喜欢 -你的决定为何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Been wondering whether I'd like it. - What's the decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一直在一起 直到鲍嘉去世\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They stayed together until Bogart passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我承认 我是年色已衰的鲍嘉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I acknowledge the... the fact that I was the old, craggy Bogey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她是一个尤物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she was this... beautiful creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美得惊人的尤物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just this stunning creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个美丽的场合 美丽的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was a beautiful place, a beautiful time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我爱这个男人爱得无法自拔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, uh, I fell head over heels in love with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她仿佛是一个完美的伴侣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She seemed to be the perfect partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知书达理 甜美 幽默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Literate, sweet, funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她当时棒极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was, uh... She was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的爱非常浓烈 你知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There wasn't any love like that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then, uh... he would...disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（达斯新闻）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 欢迎收看达斯新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello everybody, welcome to Darthn3ws.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一天的回顾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is gonna be a day one recap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在法庭里 坐在那里看现场直播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was in the courtroom, I was sitting there live, in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你们分享我的第一手感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I'm just gonna give you my first-hand account.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是法律学者 我不是律师 我这么做只是为了好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not a legal scholar, I'm not a lawyer. I do this for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我有利益相关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I have, like, a dog in the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还真的很在乎约翰尼・德普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I actually give a fuck about Johnny Depp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有男人的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And men's rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber! Amber! Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny! Johnny! Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能描述一下 你和德普先生的关系吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you describe your relationship with Mr. Depp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得他第一次打你的时候吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you remember the first time that he physically hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-记得 -请跟陪审团讲述一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes. - Please tell the jury about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远不会忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生被改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时坐在沙发上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I... I was sitting on the couch,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我询问他胳膊上的纹身的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I ask him about the tattoo he has on his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那个纹身什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't know what it said,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像模糊了 褪色的纹身很难看懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it just looked like muddled, faded tattoo that was hard to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个纹身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, the... the, um...what it, uh... a tattoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写的内容是“永远的薇诺娜”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which used to say "Winona Forever,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的前女友 薇诺娜・莱德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who was a former girlfriend, Winona Ryder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们分手的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, uh, when we broke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把最后两个字母拿掉了 然后它变成“永远的酒鬼”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took off the last two letters and had it say "Wino Forever."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为他在开玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought he was joking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为完全看不出来 纹的是那几个字 我笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because it didn't look like it said that at all, and I laughed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他一巴掌扇到我脸上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he slapped me across the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我盯着他 然后还在笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just stared at him, kind of l-laughing still,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为他也会开始笑 然后告诉我那是一个玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}thinking that he was gonna start laughing too, to tell me it was a joke,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说：“你觉得好笑吗？ 你觉得这很好笑吗 贱人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He said, "You think it's so funny? You think it's funny, bitch?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你是有趣的贱人？” 然后他又打了我一巴掌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"You think you're a funny bitch?" And he slapped me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很用力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐在那里 看着肮脏的地毯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was just sitting there looking at the dirty carpet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇自己为什么 以前没注意到地毯那么脏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wondering why I never noticed that the carpet was so filthy before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时不知道自己还能做或说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I just didn't know what else to do, I didn't know what to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道如何反应 因为我想： “天啊 他刚才是打我了吗？”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't know how to react because, "God, did he just hit me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生 你对此有何回应？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp, what is your response to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事没有发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It didn't... It... It didn't happen.
