Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.92,0:41:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你做得对 你太成熟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.48,0:41:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？你很值得敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.44,0:41:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在录音里承认打了约翰尼・德普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The fact that she's on tape admitting to hitting Johnny Depp,
