Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.00,0:41:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她还为 《华盛顿邮报》写了这篇评论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for her to have written this op-ed for The Washington Post
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.08,0:41:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且将自己推举为 “我也是”运动中的代表人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and essentially propped herself up as a figurehead in the "Me Too" movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.44,0:41:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 -可以这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Right. - So to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.60,0:41:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会有种被背叛的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, it... it... I think you... you just feel really betrayed.
