Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.48,0:41:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为家庭暴力的受害者和幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As a victim and a survivor of domestic violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.60,0:41:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这是性别歧视 但你一般都会想支持女性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}even though it's sexist, you do want to kind of back the female,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.12,0:41:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但到目前为止 我觉得她更像是侵犯者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but so far, I feel like she was more the aggressor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.84,0:41:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能都不占理 安柏可能很糟糕 你可以相信这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, they can both be wrong. Amber can be awful. You can totally believe that, 
