Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.92,0:42:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们不能以此为理由 为约翰尼・德普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we can't use that as a reason for Johnny Depp to be absolved
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.88,0:42:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开脱他所做的那些可怕的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the clearly awful things that he has done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.12,0:42:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. Cross-examination.
