Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始很尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Starting out respectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.92,0:42:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生在整个庭审过程中 都没看过你一眼 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp hasn't looked at you once this entire trial, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.72,0:42:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ooh! No, he has not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.72,0:42:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not that I've noticed, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.72,0:42:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道德普先生 为什么不回头看你吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know exactly why Mr. Depp won't look back at you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.08,0:42:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.92,0:42:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和德普先生最后的会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of the last times you ever saw Mr. Depp
