Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.52,0:42:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.64,0:42:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 直接开始放音频\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, right into audio.
