Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.92,0:43:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会再看到我的眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.40,0:43:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你和德普先生的录音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's you and Mr. Depp in that recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.72,0:43:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is.
