Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.68,0:44:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他这样做会很疯狂 因为我知道我们经历了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought it would be crazy for him to do so knowing what I know we lived through.
