Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.04,0:44:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生是你的受害者 不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp is your victim, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.68,0:44:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.24,0:44:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他离开你之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And once he left you, 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.68,0:44:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你公开称他为虐待者 这是你继续虐待他的方式 不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you continued to abuse him publicly by calling him an abuser, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.04,0:44:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个虐待者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, he is an abuser,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.32,0:44:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在网上查我们两个人 看谁才是被网络暴力的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you can look either of us up online and figure out who's being abused online.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.00,0:44:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（傻婊子）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.00,0:44:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（安柏・赫德去死）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.92,0:44:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（贱逼）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.68,0:44:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏大便！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber turd! Amber turd! Amber turd! Amber turd!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.44,0:45:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场舆论战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a battle of optics. 
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.72,0:45:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点不是法律依据 而是公众的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is not so much about the legal merits but rather what the public perception is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.68,0:45:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（德拉拉・格尔吉安 内容创造者 维尔档案播客嘉宾）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.76,0:45:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你只看公众意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you just look at public opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.88,0:45:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人真的相信安柏・赫德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}no one really believes Amber Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.32,0:45:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不买账…你相信吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't buy it for a... Do you buy this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.56,0:45:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抖音“为约翰尼・德普讨公道”的话题 有超过40亿的浏览量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The hashtag "Justice for Johnny Depp"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.60,0:45:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has more than four billion views on TikTok.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.72,0:45:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互联网已经做出了决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It seems the Internet has made up its mind
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.96,0:45:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这场庭审都还没有结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}without this court case even coming to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.20,0:45:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（约翰尼第一视角）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.00,0:45:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的回应是什么？ 在你听到赫德小姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.40,0:45:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“告诉全世界 约翰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.96,0:45:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们 约翰尼・德普
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.40,0:45:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我约翰尼・德普 一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.56,0:45:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是家庭暴力的受害者”
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.16,0:45:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说：“是的 我就是”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.24,0:46:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 安柏完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, Amber's fucked.
